od hosting, you don\'t want your blog to be slow, or, even worse, down, do you? Check out my thoughts on <a href=\"http://yoast.com/wordpress-hosting/\">WordPress hosting</a>!</p>\";s:12:\"atom_content\";s:1:\"A\";}i:10;a:15:{s:5:\"title\";s:22:\"Video SEO plugin video\";s:4:\"link\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/joostdevalk/~3/LDYf7XxKQ60/\";s:8:\"comments\";s:49:\"http://yoast.com/video-seo-plugin-video/#comments\";s:7:\"pubdate\";s:31:\"Wed, 10 Oct 2012 12:16:24 +0000\";s:2:\"dc\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";s:13:\"Joost de Valk\";}s:8:\"category\";s:3:\"SEO\";s:4:\"guid\";s:25:\"http://yoast.com/?p=49533\";s:11:\"description\";s:767:\"<p>I&#8217;ve been very hard at work with the Video SEO plugin, adding support for the most used video embed plugins for WordPress. See the changelog for specifics. The plugin is, I&#8217;m proud to say, selling well and people seem to be loving it. I&#8217;m also working on another project with the guys from Video User&#8230;</p><p><a href=\"http://yoast.com/video-seo-plugin-video/\">Video SEO plugin video</a> is a post by <a rel=\"author\" href=\"http://yoast.com/author/joost/\">Joost de Valk</a> on <a href=\"http://yoast.com\">Yoast - Tweaking Websites</a>. \n\nA good WordPress blog needs good hosting, you don\'t want your blog to be slow, or, even worse, down, do you? Check out my thoughts on <a href=\"http://yoast.com/wordpress-hosting/\">WordPress hosting</a>!</p>\";s:7:\"content\";s:24:\"Array\n			\n			\n			\n			\n		\";s:3:\"wfw\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentrss\";s:45:\"http://yoast.com/video-seo-plugin-video/feed/\";}s:5:\"slash\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";s:2:\"51\";}s:5:\"media\";a:3:{s:7:\"content\";s:4:\"\n			\";s:13:\"content_title\";s:32:\"Video SEO plugin video • Yoast\";s:19:\"content_description\";s:315:\"I&#039;ve been very hard at work with the Video SEO plugin, adding support for the most used video embed plugins for WordPress. See the changelog for specifics. The plugin is, I&#039;m proud to say, selling well and people seem to be loving it. I&#039;m also working on another project with the guys from Video User\";}s:10:\"feedburner\";a:1:{s:8:\"origlink\";s:106:\"http://yoast.com/video-seo-plugin-video/#utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=video-seo-plugin-video\";}s:7:\"summary\";s:767:\"<p>I&#8217;ve been very hard at work with the Video SEO plugin, adding support for the most used video embed plugins for WordPress. See the changelog for specifics. The plugin is, I&#8217;m proud to say, selling well and people seem to be loving it. I&#8217;m also working on another project with the guys from Video User&#8230;</p><p><a href=\"http://yoast.com/video-seo-plugin-video/\">Video SEO plugin video</a> is a post by <a rel=\"author\" href=\"http://yoast.com/author/joost/\">Joost de Valk</a> on <a href=\"http://yoast.com\">Yoast - Tweaking Websites</a>. \n\nA good WordPress blog needs good hosting, you don\'t want your blog to be slow, or, even worse, down, do you? Check out my thoughts on <a href=\"http://yoast.com/wordpress-hosting/\">WordPress hosting</a>!</p>\";s:12:\"atom_content\";s:1:\"A\";}i:11;a:15:{s:5:\"title\";s:35:\"Video SEO just became a lot easier!\";s:4:\"link\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/joostdevalk/~3/j--NgCN8Fr4/\";s:8:\"comments\";s:44:\"http://yoast.com/video-seo-release/#comments\";s:7:\"pubdate\";s:31:\"Wed, 19 Sep 2012 20:40:04 +0000\";s:2:\"dc\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";s:13:\"Joost de Valk\";}s:8:\"category\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:4:\"guid\";s:25:\"http://yoast.com/?p=46687\";s:11:\"description\";s:759:\"<p>The Video SEO plugin I have been talking about for far too long has finally been finished and released. The short version is, it&#8217;s for sale for $89, find out more here. Keep on reading for a bit of backstory. Video SEO is probably one of the most technically challenging aspects of SEO. There are&#8230;</p><p><a href=\"http://yoast.com/video-seo-release/\">Video SEO just became a lot easier!</a> is a post by <a rel=\"author\" href=\"http://yoast.