class=\"header-caption\">\r\n<h1>Wheelchair Accessible Transportation Services in Toronto.</h1>\r\n<p class=\"lead hidden-phone\">We are dedicated drivers trained to provide non-emergency wheelchair accessible transportation services to people with special needs and disabilities. We operate in Greater Toronto Area and beyond. <a href=\"/about/\"><button class=\"btn btn-primary\" type=\"button\">View More</button></a></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"fb-like\" data-href=\"http://www.facebook.com/SaveWheelchairTrans\" data-send=\"false\" data-layout=\"button_count\" data-width=\"450\" data-show-faces=\"true\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"g-plusone\" style=\"padding-top: 1px;\" data-size=\"small\" data-href=\"https://plus.google.com/106099111215835488940\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"marketing\">\r\n<h1>Your Satisfaction is Our Goal</h1>\r\n<p class=\"marketing-byline\">Need reliable wheelchair accessible transportation services? Look no further.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\r\n<div class=\"hero-unit pointbox marketing span4\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2>Your Needs</h2>\r\nOur customers always come first. You can rely on us for your travel needs:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Medical Appointments</li>\r\n	<li>Dialysis</li>\r\n	<li>Rehabilitation</li>\r\n	<li>Physiotherapy</li>\r\n	<li>Social Activities</li>\r\n	<li>School Activities</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"hero-unit pointbox marketing span4\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2>Our Services</h2>\r\nThe benefits of our services include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Professional Staff Members</li>\r\n        <li>Wheelchair Accessible Vans</li>\r\n	<li>24 / 7 Services</li>\r\n	<li>Flexible Door-to-Door Service</li>\r\n	<li>Best Rate</li>\r\n	<li>Maximum 5 Passengers</li>\r\n	<li>Provide Wheelchair if Needed</li>\r\n	<li><strong><em>Senior 10% Discount</em></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"hero-unit pointbox marketing span4\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2>Contact Us</h2>\r\nCall us for inquiries or reservations.\r\n<ul class=\"lead\">\r\n	<li>647-239-5467 (Willy)</li>\r\n	<li>647-802-8727 (Peter)</li>\r\n	<li>647-896-7400 (Chang)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nEmail us at <a href=\"mailto:info@savewheelchairtrans.com\">info@savewheelchairtrans.com</a>.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Home','','inherit','closed','open','','14-autosave','','','2013-02-16 01:13:11','2013-02-16 06:13:11','',14,'http://savewheelchairtrans.com/14-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(173,1,'2013-01-25 07:04:22','2013-01-25 07:04:22','    <header class=\'header-background\'>\r\n      <img src=\'wp-content/uploads/2013/01/wheelchair.jpg\' alt=\'wheelchair transportation\'>\r\n      <div class=\'container\'>\r\n        <div class=\'header-caption\'>\r\n          <h1>\r\n            Non-Emergency Wheelchair Accessible Transportation Services in <abbr title=\'Greater Toronto Area\'>GTA</abbr>.\r\n          </h1>\r\n          <p class=\'lead hidden-phone\'>\r\n            We are dedicated drivers trained to provide wheelchair-accessible transportation services to people with special needs and disabilities. We operate in Greater Toronto Area and beyond. <a href=\'/about/\'><button class=\'btn btn-primary\' type=\'button\'>View More</button></a>\r\n            <div class=\"fb-like\" data-href=\"http://www.facebook.com/SaveWheelchairTrans\" data-send=\"false\" data-layout=\"button_count\" data-width=\"450\" data-show-faces=\"true\"></div>\r\n            <div style=\'padding-top:1px\' class=\"g-plusone\" data-size=\"small\" data-href=\"https://plus.google.com/106099111215835488940\"></div>\r\n          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </header>\r\n    <div class=\'container\'>\r\n      <div class=\'marketing\'>\r\n        <h1>Your Satisfaction is Our Goal</h1>\r\n        <p class=\'marketing-byline\'>\r\n          Need reliable wheelchair-accessible transportation services? Look no further.\r\n        </p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\'container\'>\r\n      <div class=\'row-fluid\'>\r\n        <div class=\'hero-unit pointbox marketing span4\' style=\'text-align:left\'>\r\n          <h2>Your Needs</h2>\r\n          <p>Our customers always come first. You can rely on us for your travel needs:</p>\r\n          <ul>\r\n            <li>Medical Appointments</li>\r\n            <li>Dialysis</li>\r\n            <li>Rehabilitation</li>\r\n            <li>Physiotherapy</li>\r\n            <li>Social Activities</li>\r\n            <li>School Activities</li>\r\n          </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\'hero-unit pointbox marketing span4\' style=\'text-align:left\'>\r\n          <h2>Our Services</h2>\r\n          <p>The benefits of our services include:</p>\r\n          <ul>\r\n            <li>Professional Staff Members</li>\r\n            <li>24 / 7 Services</li>\r\n            <li>Flexible Door-to-Door Service</li>\r\n            <li>Best Rate</li>\r\n            <li>Maximum 5 Passengers</li>\r\n            <li>Provide Wheelchair if Needed</li>\r\n            <li><strong><em>Senior 10% Discount</em></strong></li>\r\n          </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\'hero-unit pointbox marketing span4\' style=\'text-align:left\'>\r\n          <h2>Contact Us</h2>\r\n          <p>Call us for inquiries or reservations.</p>\r\n          <ul class=\'lead\'>\r\n            <li>647-239-5467 (Willy)</li>\r\n            <li>647-802-8727 (Peter)</li>\r\n            <li>647-896-7400 (Chang)</li>\r\n          </ul>\r\n          <p>Email us at <a href=\'mailto:info@savewheelchairtrans.com\'>info@savewheelchairtrans.com</a>.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>','Home','','inherit','closed','open','','14-revision-4','','','2013-01-25 07:04:22','2013-01-25 07:04:22','',14,'http://savewheelchairtrans.com/14-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(181,1,'2013-02-21 20:47:04','2013-02-22 01:47:04','I originally found the StopGap project from <a href=\"http://www.thestar.com/life/2013/01/03/toronto_businesses_get_free_ramps_and_new_customers_in_wheelchairs.html\">an article in Toronto Star</a>, and I found this project truly inspiring.\r\n\r\nStopGap is a non-profit organization to remove the physical barriers so that every person can access every space without worries. And their first project is the community ramp project: build bright colourful ramps with donated materials and install them at the stores that are willing to have the ramps in their doorsteps.\r\n\r\nWhat I really like about this project is the attention that this little ramp can get; the ramp itself is probably not the best wheelchair ramp design ever, but its vivid colour with StopGap website address on it attracts people\'s attentions nearby. Also I could see that these ramps also give positive images to the local stores that have them. I think this project could raise curiosity and awareness of accessibility issues, which is what we need to make our neighbourhood more accessible.\r\n\r\nHere are some pictures that we took while we were at Stouffville. StopGap is expanding to install the ramps on other towns, and you can see the full list of locations <a href=\"http://www.stopgapblog.blogspot.ca/p/ramp-locations.html\">here</a>.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_166\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<a href=\"http://savewheelchairtrans.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/b07ef10a5cfd11e2a52022000a1f9e5e_7.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-166\" alt=\"yellow ramp\" src=\"http://savewheelchairtrans.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/b07ef10a5cfd11e2a52022000a1f9e5e_7-300x300.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a> yellow ramp.[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<a href=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-bFFC2OkssPk/UR8ByBZgzjI/AAAAAAAAAOk/2FDp-lAcrnI/s525/6da8099c5cfe11e2b68522000a1fb1ee_7.jpg\"><img alt=\"ramps\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-bFFC2OkssPk/UR8ByBZgzjI/AAAAAAAAAOk/2FDp-lAcrnI/s525/6da8099c5cfe11e2b68522000a1fb1ee_7.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a> ramps[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<a href=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-c3E5Cj87YnI/UR8ByK_OV0I/AAAAAAAAAOo/XD_glhxsW9A/s525/7d250a5a5cfe11e2aacd22000a1f932c_7.jpg\"><img alt=\"red ramp\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-c3E5Cj87YnI/UR8ByK_OV0I/AAAAAAAAAOo/XD_glhxsW9A/s525/7d250a5a5cfe11e2aacd22000a1f932c_7.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a> red ramp[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<a href=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-Kru9fTTzyQI/UR8BzG7qgyI/AAAAAAAAAO0/Ht7dSJQG2yo/s525/d6c0db205cfe11e292a022000a1faf61_7.jpg\"><img alt=\"stouffville go station\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-Kru9fTTzyQI/UR8BzG7qgyI/AAAAAAAAAO0/Ht7dSJQG2yo/s525/d6c0db205cfe11e292a022000a1faf61_7.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a> stouffville go station[/caption]','The Community Ramp Project - StopGap','','inherit','closed','open','','165-revision-7','','','2013-02-21 20:47:04','2013-02-22 01:47:04','',165,'http://savewheelchairtrans.com/165-revision-7/',0,'revision','',0),(180,1,'2013-02-15 23:07:22','2013-02-16 04:07:22','I originally found the StopGap project from <a href=\"http://www.thestar.com/life/2013/01/03/toronto_businesses_get_free_ramps_and_new_customers_in_wheelchairs.html\">an article in Toronto Star</a>, and I found this project truly inspiring.\r\n\r\nStopGap is a non-profit organization to remove the physical barriers so that every person can access every space without worries. And their first project is the community ramp project: build bright colourful ramps with donated materials and install them at the stores that are willing to have the ramps in their doorsteps.\r\n\r\nWhat I really like about this project is the attention that this little ramp can get; the ramp itself is probably not the best wheelchair ramp design ever, but its vivid colour with StopGap website addr